# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Video production — per-lesson HyperFrames build workspaces (HTML sources,
# caches, renders). Local-only: active builds live in lessons/<stem>/, delivered
# ones move to lessons/_archive/<stem>/ (see that folder's README.md).
# Final deliverables live in projects/video-production/videos/ (tracked).
projects/video-production/lessons/*
!projects/video-production/lessons/README.md
